    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すずの様子が気になってメッセージをしたが\n返事がないな……心配だから、様子を見に来たが……",
      "startTime": 3.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ミルクを流し込んで……こうして、こうですわ！\n……やりました。うまく出来ましたわ！",
      "startTime": 16.4478908221,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drink-02.m4a",
          "delay": 182.1538924999988,
          "startTime": 9.0478908221
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "数日でここまで出来るようになるなんて\nやはり私は天才ですわね",
      "startTime": 23.9145574887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……って{user}さん！？\nいつからそこに居たんですの！？",
      "startTime": 29.1812241554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、さっき来たばかりだが……\nすずこそキッチンで何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 34.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "よくぞ聞いてくれましたわ！　これはラテアートですの\nコーヒーの上にミルクで絵を描くんですのよ",
      "startTime": 42.7425391833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい、この完璧なハート型を！　ラテアートの\nために道具を買い揃えた甲斐がありましたわ",
      "startTime": 52.0092058499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ……すずがラテアートにハマっていたなんて\n知らなかったよ",
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "チノがやっていたのを思い出して興味がわいたのですわ\nそれでずっと練習していたんです",
      "startTime": 65.7600673358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！　せっかくですから\nラテアートの練習を手伝ってくださいまし",
      "startTime": 72.4267340024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "手伝うのは構わないが、何をすればいいんだ？",
      "startTime": 75.9496147474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "難しいことはありませんわ\n私の作ったカフェラテを飲んで下さるだけで結構です",
      "startTime": 82.393763272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "練習とはいえ、せっかく作ったカフェラテを\n飲まずに捨てるのはもったいないでしょう？",
      "startTime": 90.7270966053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、確かにもったいないな\n分かった、このカフェラテは俺が飲ませてもらうよ",
      "startTime": 97.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、今日作った分が後七杯ありますから\nそれも全部差し上げますわ",
      "startTime": 105.4080943902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "七杯！？　そんなに沢山カフェラテを作ったのか！？",
      "startTime": 108.0392068386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "上達するには回数をこなすのが一番ですから\n毎日大量に作って寮のみなさんに振る舞っています",
      "startTime": 116.6590918541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "ただ最近、私がカフェラテを淹れ始めるとみんな足早に\nリビングから出て行くようになってしまったんですの",
      "startTime": 126.8257585208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "その気持ちは分かるよ\nこの量……お腹がたぷたぷになりそうだ……",
      "startTime": 133.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 138.4614742915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……折り入って\nお願いしたいことがあるのですが……",
      "startTime": 143.2102480571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えーと……今日は仕事が忙しいから\nカフェラテを飲む手伝いはちょっと……",
      "startTime": 149.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "そういうお願いではありませんわ\n実は私……喫茶店でアルバイトをしたいのです",
      "startTime": 156.4843191783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "アルバイト？　どうしてまた急に……\n何か、お金が必要なことでもあるのか？",
      "startTime": 166.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "違いますわ！　その……\n単刀直入に言うと、ラテアートの勉強がしたいのですわ",
      "startTime": 174.0174029033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "独学では限界がありますから\nもっとうまくなるためにバリスタの下で学びたいのです",
      "startTime": 183.5174008687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、バイトする喫茶店の候補も考えてあります\nこのチラシを見てくださいまし",
      "startTime": 193.0174008687,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5708.841228799997,
          "startTime": 194.1840675354
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になっているスタイリストさんから\n私にぴったりのお店があると紹介されたのですわ",
      "startTime": 198.4174029033,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6649.2637634,
          "startTime": 205.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "これがその喫茶店のチラシか。なになに……\n『いもうとメイド喫茶』……",
      "startTime": 207.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すず……ここで働いても\nそんなにラテアートの勉強にはならないと思うぞ……",
      "startTime": 212.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！　そうなんですの！？\nでは、他の喫茶店を調べますわ……！",
      "startTime": 219.7017315228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "話は分かった。だが、すずはまだ中学生だ\nバイトはもうしばらく待ってもいいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 227.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "ですが、私はラテアートがうまくなりたいんです！\n……いえ、それだけではありませんわね",
      "startTime": 236.0135905901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんと一緒にラビットハウスで働いた時\n私は本当に楽しかったんです",
      "startTime": 243.7135905901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_11_03-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風に、素敵な喫茶店でお客さんや仲間と\n交流する楽しさを、また味わいたいのですわ",
      "startTime": 252.2135905901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
